Packages needed for installation on opensuse 11.2:

mysql >= 5.1
python-mysql
python-django

(not sure if we will use matplotlib or google charts)
python-matplotlib
python-django-googlecharts

Mysql settings:





installation:

start mysql
log into mysql as an admin:
  grant all on *.* to koubat;

log into mysql as koubat:
  create database goove;
  #grant all on goove.* to 'koubat'@'localhost';
  #flush privileges;

python manage.py syncdb

		

